      "order_number": 0,
      "text": "Hey, Claudia, how are you doing?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 600.81,
      "start_time": 600.17,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 1,
      "text": "Hey, Nick."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 601.26,
      "start_time": 600.82,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 2,
      "text": "Good."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 602.07,
      "start_time": 601.27,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "How are you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 603.05,
      "start_time": 602.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 4,
      "text": "Not too bad."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 604.27,
      "start_time": 603.06,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 5,
      "text": "I catch you in the middle of lunch."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 606.49,
      "start_time": 605.86,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 6,
      "text": "Yeah,"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 609.86,
      "start_time": 607.7,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "I saw, I saw the cleaning of the teeth though."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 610.57,
      "start_time": 609.89,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "You're all?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 615.17,
      "start_time": 612.19,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "I saw it and I was like, oh, this guy just stayed in the laundry."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 618.86,
      "start_time": 616.91,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "I know I was in the break room and I'm like, uh,"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 620.79,
      "start_time": 619.9,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "no, it's all good."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 622.48,
      "start_time": 620.8,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 12,
      "text": "I just like, this one should be nice and easy."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 626.9,
      "start_time": 622.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "Like this is really your time to connect with me and how have things been going?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 628.65,
      "start_time": 628.05,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "Good."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 629.75,
      "start_time": 628.66,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "Good, good, good."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 631.75,
      "start_time": 629.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "Have I had a chance to play with it?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 632.83,
      "start_time": 631.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 633.96,
      "start_time": 633.09,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "Ok."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 635.87,
      "start_time": 634.12,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "So we just, we gotta punt this one."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 638.83,
      "start_time": 637.98,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "You wanna do that?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 646.55,
      "start_time": 639.08,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 21,
      "text": "Yeah, let's punt it because I want you to have some time to be able to play with it and then we can talk about the stuff that you need to accomplish that you're having a problem with."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 647.95,
      "start_time": 647.57,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "Let's do that."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 648.76,
      "start_time": 648.41,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 23,
      "text": "Ok."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 650.59,
      "start_time": 648.99,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 24,
      "text": "What's a good time or a date?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 654.13,
      "start_time": 651.47,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 25,
      "text": "Uh, how is next week on the 13th?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 658.15,
      "start_time": 657.53,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 26,
      "text": "Perfect."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 659.25,
      "start_time": 658.26,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 27,
      "text": "Ah, I'm not here."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 660.09,
      "start_time": 659.54,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 28,
      "text": "You're not here."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 661.79,
      "start_time": 660.1,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 29,
      "text": "What about the 15th?"
