      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 48,
      "text": "Just Orlando?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 696.84,
      "start_time": 695.06,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 49,
      "text": "Just going to Orlando?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 698,
      "start_time": 697.04,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 50,
      "text": "You gonna do Disney?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 700.26,
      "start_time": 698.59,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 51,
      "text": "Uh Universal"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 701.07,
      "start_time": 700.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 52,
      "text": "Universal?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 701.46,
      "start_time": 701.08,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 53,
      "text": "Ok."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 704.81,
      "start_time": 701.47,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 54,
      "text": "Islands of Adventure or uh Universal Studios?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 705.59,
      "start_time": 704.82,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 55,
      "text": "Oh, you're doing both?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 706.06,
      "start_time": 705.6,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 56,
      "text": "Ok."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 707.16,
      "start_time": 706.41,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 57,
      "text": "We're doing both."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 710.86,
      "start_time": 707.17,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 58,
      "text": "And then we want to go to the, um, what is it?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 712.02,
      "start_time": 710.87,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 59,
      "text": "The Kennedy Space"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 712.42,
      "start_time": 712.03,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 60,
      "text": "Center."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 712.95,
      "start_time": 712.67,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 61,
      "text": "Yep."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 713.29,
      "start_time": 712.97,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 62,
      "text": "Kennedy."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 715.38,
      "start_time": 713.52,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 63,
      "text": "Isn't that, that's Cape Canaveral though, isn't it?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 716.66,
      "start_time": 715.97,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 64,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 717.06,
      "start_time": 716.67,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 65,
      "text": "So"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 717.75,
      "start_time": 717.07,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 66,
      "text": "maybe on the way"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 718.37,
      "start_time": 717.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 67,
      "text": "back."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 718.75,
      "start_time": 718.58,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 68,
      "text": "Ok."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 719.38,
      "start_time": 718.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 69,
      "text": "Got it."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 720.78,
      "start_time": 720.01,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 70,
      "text": "And, uh,"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 732.05,
      "start_time": 722.09,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 71,
      "text": "what, so what I I'm genuinely curious with, with the Universal, what are you looking forward to the most like Harry Potter World or the Marvel Place or the, like, what, what, what are you looking forward to,"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 737.29,
      "start_time": 732.58,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 72,
      "text": "to be honest, the last time that I was there, I was in high school."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 741.27,
      "start_time": 737.77,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 73,
      "text": "This was, I graduated high school in 09."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 745.43,
      "start_time": 741.97,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 74,
      "text": "So I don't know what's about 12 years, 13 years maybe."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 749.83,
      "start_time": 746.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 75,
      "text": "Uh, so I have no idea of what is in the parks now."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 757.53,
      "start_time": 750.35,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 76,
      "text": "Uh, we're doing it more to just get out of Miami for a little bit but not super crazy into rides."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 761.67,
      "start_time": 757.54,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 77,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my wife and I were talking, we're like, I don't know, do you think we're too old for this?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 762.01,
      "start_time": 761.68,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 78,
      "text": "You know,"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 768.19,
      "start_time": 763.39,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 79,
      "text": "I was gonna say not being super into rides is probably gonna be kind of a downside going to Universal."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 778.86,
      "start_time": 768.5,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 80,
      "text": "Uh because there are a lot of rides at the Universal but at the same time, like it's still unbelievably themed, it'll be super fun like I did."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 780.83,
      "start_time": 778.88,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 81,
      "text": "Uh So I believe it or not."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 785.59,
      "start_time": 780.84,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 82,
      "text": "I've, I've, so I've been to Universal Islands of Adventure where all like the superhero stuff was."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 790.4,
      "start_time": 785.6,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 83,
      "text": "I've never done Harry Potter World, but I did go to Universal Studios in Singapore."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 795.54,
      "start_time": 792.2,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 84,
      "text": "Yeah, I was out there, I was out there on my honeymoon."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 802.38,
      "start_time": 795.55,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 85,
      "text": "We went to Singapore and Bali and I'm a big ride guy, like a big roller coaster guy."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 809.01,
      "start_time": 802.72,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 86,
      "text": "And it was like, if we're going out to, if we're going on a honeymoon, I have to hit at least one theme park."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 813.63,
      "start_time": 809.02,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 87,
      "text": "And the, the one that I had access to was Universal Studios in Singapore."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 814.31,
      "start_time": 813.64,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 88,
      "text": "So I did that"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 815.72,
      "start_time": 814.96,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 89,
      "text": "nice."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 817.46,
      "start_time": 815.73,
      "recording_attendee_id": "0dda40d9-f785-49e2-9dcb-fad53c809d98",
      "order_number": 90,
      "text": "And how does it compare to the one here?"
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 826.47,
      "start_time": 819.01,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 91,
      "text": "Uh The rides are significantly smaller than the ones that we got in the States."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 833.73,
      "start_time": 826.48,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 92,
      "text": "But it's like, I in a, in a real way, it's like almost better themed, but it's also behind if this makes sense."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 839.51,
      "start_time": 833.74,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 93,
      "text": "So like, and what I mean by this is like the Singapore one had like areas that were themed for like the mummy."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 846.31,
      "start_time": 840.01,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 94,
      "text": "Like you remember like the Brendan Frasier movies, the mummy, like, they have like an entire area that's themed after that."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 849.25,
      "start_time": 846.41,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 95,
      "text": "They have an entire area that's themed after Shrek."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
      "recording_id": "1e209cdb-9145-48d0-8a23-a12a49991f50",
      "end_time": 852.28,
      "start_time": 851.33,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9afc9650-7167-4108-ac6c-759894d9ffc7",
      "order_number": 96,
      "text": "They have an entire area."
    },
    {
      "id": "302afd14-6856-4e66-a9eb-a0096927f6e7",
